					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">For comparison, Time Lord used sprites for masking, low-priority sprites behind the scenery to mask just like SMB3.  (Time Lord also has that impossible Mexican boss whose health regenerates quickly, and you need a turbo controller to beat him.  Maybe that's why a used copy only goes for $1.)
<br />
<br />Neat video.  Really crappy production values, but they didn't exactly have Final Cut Pro back in 1990.  Only major problem with the video is the voice recording, the people are very hard to hear.</div>

					
